item.title: Telangana: Man dies, two injured in road accident in Jogulamba Gadwal
item.description:
<![CDATA[Telangana: Man dies, two injured in road accident in Jogulamba Gadwal
Bhushan Reddy and two others were heading to Gangaram in Pebbair mandal, on a two wheeler. At Jinkalapally stage, the two-wheeler was hit by unidentified vehicle, resulting in the spot death of Timamma
By Telangana Today Published Date - 15 May 2025, 10:50 AM
